This is betrayal, Kurt, okay?

39:32.709 --> 39:34.710
This is exactly how
friends break up.

39:34.744 --> 39:36.779
She auditioned for
your understudy, Rachel.

39:36.813 --> 39:38.380
How is that betrayal?
Okay, you know what?

39:38.415 --> 39:40.349
Let me break it down for you...
the sole purpose

39:40.383 --> 39:41.817
of an understudy is to hope

39:41.852 --> 39:43.752
that the lead never goes on.

39:43.787 --> 39:45.054
She only wins if I lose!

39:45.088 --> 39:46.822
And I can't be around this
negative energy anymore.

39:46.857 --> 39:49.058
This is my big break
and she is poisoning it!

39:49.092 --> 39:50.593
"Poison."

39:50.627 --> 39:51.894
Even if she never went out
on that stage,

39:51.928 --> 39:53.696
this would be
a very important job for her.

39:53.730 --> 39:54.964
And I'm a little disappointed
you can't find

39:54.998 --> 39:56.232
the generosity
in your heart to see that.

39:56.266 --> 39:57.766
You know what? If you think

39:57.801 --> 39:59.635
