off of my star sandwich,

40:04.241 --> 40:06.542
then you are naive
and willfully ignorant!

40:06.576 --> 40:08.244
She would kill for this part!

40:08.278 --> 40:09.645
Oh, yes, she has been
awful to us before.

40:09.679 --> 40:10.813
But I believe her now.

40:10.847 --> 40:12.615
