all happy and supportive.

40:29.733 --> 40:30.900
But it's all crap!

40:30.934 --> 40:32.534
Because you and I have
never been friends.

40:32.569 --> 40:35.271
Never have and never will be!

40:35.305 --> 40:37.139
Rachel, no.

40:37.173 --> 40:39.441
No. No, you know what?
Let her go.

40:39.476 --> 40:42.878
